The paper proposes a new approach for density estimation using neural autoregressive flows, which is a combination of normalizing flows and autoregressive models. This makes it likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and systems and control (cs.SD).
